{"type":"message","id":"c44e2096","parentId":"e7c53b49","timestamp":"2026-02-28T07:16:25.873Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我现在找到了两个配置文件：\n\n1. `~/.config/opencode/opencode.json` - 这是 OpenCode 的主配置文件，目前只配置了插件\n2. `~/.opencode/config.json` - 这是我之前创建的 oh-my-opencode 配置文件\n\n但用户问的是\"opencode里，kimi-coding模型的配置\"。让我检查一下是否有其他的配置文件，比如 `~/.config/opencode/oh-my-opencode.json` 或者 `~/.config/opencode/opencode.jsonc`。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:205","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find ~/.config/opencode -name \"*.json\" -o -name \"*.jsonc\" 2>/dev/null | grep -v node_modules"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:206","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la ~/.config/opencode/ | grep -v node_modules"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:207","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.config/opencode/oh-my-opencode.json 2>/dev/null || echo \"文件不存在\""}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:208","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.config/opencode/opencode.jsonc 2>/dev/null || echo \"文件不存在\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":80569,"output":339,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80908,"cost":{"input":0.0000080569,"output":6.78e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000081247}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772262971352}}
