{"type":"message","id":"3008cbc5","parentId":"21ca537b","timestamp":"2026-02-28T07:28:15.695Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"根据搜索结果，我找到了大量关于 xiaodouya (小豆芽) 的代码和文档。让我整理一下当前 xiaodouya MCP 的状态。\n\n从搜索结果可以看到：\n1. 有一个 `xiaodouya_mcp_server.py` 文件\n2. 有 PowerShell 函数文件 `xiaodouya_functions.ps1`\n3. 有测试执行日志\n4. 有分析报告\n\n让我检查一下 MCP server 的状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"根据搜索结果，我找到了关于 **xiaodouya (小豆芽)** MCP 的相关文件和状态：\n\n## 📁 小豆芽 MCP 相关文件\n\n### 主要文件位置：`~/.openclaw/workspace/`\n\n| 文件 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `xiaodouya/xiaodouya_mcp_server.py` | **MCP Server 主程序** |\n| `xiaodouya_functions.ps1` | PowerShell 函数库 |\n| `xiaodouya_control_fixed.py` | Python 控制器（修复版） |\n| `xiaodouya_aliases.sh` | Bash 别名脚本 |\n| `xiaodouya_controls_analysis.md` | UI 控件分析报告 |\n| `xiaodouya_test_execution_log.md` | **测试执行日志** |\n\n---\n\n## 🔍 MCP Server 当前状态\n\n让我检查 MCP Server 是否正在运行："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:213","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ps aux | grep -i \"xiaodouya\\|mcp\" | grep -v grep"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:214","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace/xiaodouya/xiaodouya_mcp_server.py | head -50"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read:215","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/yirongbest/.openclaw/workspace/xiaodouya_test_execution_log.md","limit":100}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":94448,"output":487,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94935,"cost":{"input":0.0000094448,"output":9.74e-8,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000095422}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772263613291}}
